Class A_Currency

  • java.lang.Object
    • task6.money.A_Currency
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    A_CurrencyCoin, A_CurrencyPaper

    public abstract class A_Currency
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<A_Currency>
    Defines the shared elements of a currency denomination that can represent any unit of coin or bill; e.g., dime, nickel, single, five.
